&CP2K  
  PROGRAM   FIST
  PROJECT   deca_ala
  IOLEVEL   1
  FFTLIB    FFTSG
  RUN_TYPE   md
&END

&MD
  ensemble:     nve                    ensemble type (nve,nvt,npt_i,npt_f)
  steps:        10                     total number of steps
  timestep:     2.5 fs                 time step [fs]
  temperature:  298                    temperature [K]
  restart:      init                   start type (init,pos,posvel)
  constraints   on
  print  files        100
  print  screen       1
&END

&TOPOLOGY
 FOFI_FIL        par_all27_prot_lipid.inp
 FORCEFIELD      CHM
 COORDINATE      PDB
 COORD_FILE_NAME deca_ala.pdb
&END

&EWALD
 units angstrom
 ewald_type ewald
 ewald_param .44 21 6
&END

&FORCE_FIELD
 torsions
   jorgensen  HA CT3 CT1 NH1 1.0 0.0
   jorgensen  HA CT3 CT1  HB 2.0 0.0
   jorgensen  HA CT3 CT1   C 3.0 0.0
 end
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          100.0 100.0 100.0
&END

